  "title" : "Altering value in a class file",
  "body" : "<p>With ClassEditor I'm able to change values of constants but is it possible to alter the code where a value is being set?</p>\n\n<p>Here's an example code that appears on the file:</p>\n\n<pre><code>this.varr[this.sval] = 11;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>How can I edit the file so that instead of setting 11 as the value, I can set 33?</p>\n"
